@node Historia "History of the program"

                                @{b}History@{ub}

1.0 97-Apr-20  - Added Date structure, saving and calculating of an
average.

1.0 97-Apr-28  - Added possibility of displaying exact date's data.

1.1 97-May-02  - Commodities added, window instead of text file.

1.11 97-Jun-07 - A lot of improvements (big thanks to LeMUr!), commo-
dities  improved,  hastened  displaying  of  a data in the window, I/O
operation  buffered,  counting  the time when the window is opened too
and some small things that I have forgotten.

1.11 97-Jun-27 - Added calculating of an average of the last month,
small modification in GUI (text-type and 'About' gadgets added).

1.11 97-Jul-13 - Changed the bug which caused that the program used to
write to the log file the same day a few times.

1.12 97-Jul-27 - Triton.library replaced by muimaster.library, changed
the  procedure  used  for  calculation  of  an  average (it's reliable
now...).

1.13 97-Aug-23 - Used MUI broker instead of my own-the less the better
for the system.

1.15 97-Sep-02 - CHARTS !!!

1.16 97-Oct-13 - Blabla.library and reqtools.library replaced by
asl.library  and  intuition.library (back to the sources !).  Improved
charts and the program reaction for New Year (it's not going to have a
party ;)).

1.17 97-Nov-11 - A few small bugs removed as well as additional proce-
dure-charts  are  more precise now, a possibility of changing a disk's
validation is highly reduced

1.18 04-Feb-98 - A lot of things improved: problems with 'Quit' option
(DailyUp  used  to suspend itself), 'Logins&Logouts' charts, delays in
reactions for hotkeys pressed and some more.  Added:  new preferences'
window,   columns   in  ListView  gadget,  memory's  allocation  using
LibAllocPooled(), time displayed in minutes and seconds (before it was
as a fraction), new type of graph (bars)...

1.19 15-Feb-98 - Added possibility of choosing the directory for log
files (now it can be stored not only in S:), iconification improved as
well as location of an objects in preferences window.

1.19 22-Feb-98 - Removed a bug that caused errors in an average of a
week on charts, major commodities' modification, own system is created
at  the  start  of the program and than, it's replaced by MUI based-it
saves  memory  (there's no need to load MUI), one bug removed-it could
cause  a  lot  of troubles..., ToFile() procedure improved (it used to
delete  file  indicator  and reset the system-it should be fp=0 but it
was fh=0).

1.20 05-Apr-98 - Added MultiUser's support and localisation, improved
(once  again)  procedure used to create the list of days which is used
to   create   charts   (I  hope  it's  OK  now  ;),  GUI  changed-used
RegisterGroup  which allowed to use one window instead of three, added
grid in charts' window, changed the way of month's selection.


@endnode

